    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant, delivering 333hp with a 7,900 RPM redline. This example retains its factory-spec individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS system, ensuring sharp throttle response across the power band. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded Bilstein dampers. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity and rotational balance of this driver-focused machine remain exceptional.",
      "price": 32500.0,
